In the middle of a deadly pandemic, some leftists are still laser-focused on dividing Americans along racial lines.
The entire country has been affected by the novel coronavirus, but some leftists are pushing the narrative that the coronavirus is hurting minority groups to a larger extent than the white population.
Gavin Newsom said the current data does not support that narrative.
In California, at least 16,957 people have tested positive for the Wuhan coronavirus.
